span style=\"color: red;\">瞄準頭部射擊</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映：</span></span><br />\n示威者吐血<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhRCPds07zSM&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpDMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=6262496c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM</a> <br />\n<br />\n拖行暈倒示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGfhHJqNVPig&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpDMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=20f070d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig</a> <br />\n<br />\n唔比救護車入<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmT8SH2EJctk&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpDMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=6631782b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk</a> <br />\n<br />\n地鐵站噴椒<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsQk9mLw07WM&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpDMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=1dee22a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM</a> <br />\n<br />\n開槍<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9bbFANmVWZ4&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpDMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=0b3b9044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4</a> <br />\n<br />\n向記者放tear gas<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcWZ0R67V5Yg&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpDMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=50523652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg</a> <br />\n<br />\n事後嚟張大合照慶功先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3BUJgDg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3BUJgDg.png&h=d811719e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強烈建議告上聯合國！向對示威者施過度武力嘅警察懲處！終生不得踏入歐美國家半步！呢班人渣注定世世代代共享中國人嘅榮耀</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:43:12.000Z","msg":"為放便whatsapp send出去，所以盡量少片同gif"},{"pid":"cb58d7b8babea861fa3f9bea0dfb20d5f3d5e4a1","tid":1221334,"uid":17700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:43:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb4b23d02baed61959fc2b54fd60643106bae9b7","tid":1221334,"uid":17700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:43:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"200cc3abd7ffc26530d1ac6db0034e12f9e1cb77","tid":1221334,"uid":17700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:44:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8ee763a3b48407181eedf9a9ec0caf5f1422f32","tid":1221334,"uid":17700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:45:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8df31110f2c87df604a3a09013524a9e7eac5698","tid":1221334,"uid":17700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:45:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e207968f5e33491058a26e0eb0eaaf0dde39c85f","tid":1221334,"uid":17700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:45:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e3f9fbb90a54c381e10002d4cb1e28bb470d222","tid":1221334,"uid":17700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:46:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6fba1914dd2dce85e7d8fb6e0d9dc4113acb07a9","tid":1221334,"uid":17700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:46:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cf00403297b33bafb0af809c0e833f83f546be7b","tid":1221334,"uid":17700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:47:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"21cf2950c0229e07e7a030f10c4d85a04bbbfae4","tid":1221334,"uid":17700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi